It is the number of 4-by-4 [[magic square]]s.<ref>{{cite web|title=Sloane's A006052 : Number of magic squares of order n composed of the numbers from 1 to n^2, counted up to rotations and reflections|url=https://oeis.org/A006052|website=The On-Line Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences|publisher=OEIS Foundation|accessdate=2016-06-02}}</ref> It is a [[Harshad number]].

880 is the frequency in [[hertz]] of the [[musical note]] A5.

'''880''' is also:
* The code for [[international direct dialing]] phone calls to [[Telephone numbers in Bangladesh|Bangladesh]]
* The year [[880 BC]] or [[880|AD 880]].
* [[Interstate 880]], an [[Interstate Highway System|Interstate highway]] in the [[San Francisco Bay Area]].
* [[Dodge Custom 880]], an automobile manufactured from 1962 to 1965.

